This really cool digital watch from Kenneth Cole is unbiased towards gender and can be worn by either men or women. Not exactly a conservative looking watch this model from Kenneth Cole is trendy and would be the perfect accessory to be worn with your casual wear. Sport it to a fashion show a party or an informal affair and you’ll have heads turning to catch a glimpse of this good looking timepiece sitting gorgeously on your wrist. This watch is not just good looking but also extremely accurate and reliable because of the quartz mechanism which it runs on.

Body and Design

This Kenneth Cole digital watch features a rather sleek and stylish round positive LCD dial with large sized digits appearing on the screen for easy readability. The dial is placed in an exquisite stainless steel case which adds to the glam value of the watch. The overall look of the watch case is completed by the smooth and perforated leather strap that is fastened onto your hand with a buckle clasp. The watch glass is made of a highly impact and scratch resistant mineral crystal material.

This watch is technologically more advanced than most digital watches are with its state of the art Digi-Touch touch screen technology which enables the user to use the functions of this watch by just a touch instead of the regular push buttons found on regular digital watches.The watch has a thickness of 11.2 mm and a watch case diameter of 44 mm giving it the appropriate size to qualify as a unisex watch.

Functions and Other Features

It features all the basic functions that are expected of a good quality digital watch you can view the time day date and month in a single glance saving you the time and effort needed to look into a calendar for the later functions.

Since even more people with a phobia for analog watch hands have started globe-trotting it has become an important part of every decent digital watch to possess a world time and this Kenneth Cole watch scores in that field too by featuring a 32 city world timer which lets you know what time it is half way across the globe which means you don’t have to set and reset the time as soon as you land in a different country anymore.

If you had to time your morning jog this digital watch lets you do that too with its stopwatch and digital chronograph function which also features a countdown timer. If you were in a dark theatre and wanted to know the time this digital watch is up to the task with its brilliant EL backlight. Whether you are a stylish fashionista or employed in a MNC sporting a timepiece like this sure to have heads turning as you walk by.
